questions: Who has been treated with the care plan with the code {careplan_code}?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX snomed: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#snomed:SNOMED-CT> SELECT DISTINCT ?first ?last WHERE {{ ?careplan a syn:CarePlan; syn:code '{careplan_code}'^^snomed:; syn:patientId ?patientid. ?patient a syn:Patient; syn:id ?patientid; syn:first ?first ; syn:last ?last .}}
